What is a Knolx session ?
=================================
Knolx session is a knowledge sharing session wherein all Knolders meet
at a point of time for a period of 45 minutes to 60 minutes once every
week during which one of the Knolders presents on a technology to either
introduce it to other Knolders or to discuss about its pros and cons.


What is Knolx Portal ?
=================================
Knolx portal is a Knolx management portal which helps in scheduling these
sessions, getting feedback on scheduled sessions and thereby providing
meaningful information to the presenter.


Framework
=================================
Knolx portal is build using Play 2.6.0 which can be packaged using
`activator dist`.
